Nanna
Nana
Nanna Neprsdóttir
Nanna, Daughter of Nepr
Norse Goddess

Although she doesn't make any appearance in-game, she is mentioned for the first time by Brok in God of War (2018). Nanna is likely living among her fellow Aesir gods in the Great Lodge. She survived Ragnarök and later settled in Vanaheim with the survivors.
